As Quickstride and Windlord move around outside LORD ELDER came over
to thier location, his alt mode that of a large dog with brown and
black spots. However now there was metallic armor as well, he was
transmtealled. In this mode he moved easily over the rough terrain to
follow the two Maximals.

As he arrived at thier location he transfomred to robot mode.
"Quickstride, you do realize that the meeting never ended, but you
just walked out of it?" LORDE ELDER looked at QUICKSTRIDE and then at
WINDLORD, "Weren't we suppose to be retrieving Windlord and coming
back?"

-------------------------------

There is a beep on TUSCON's comm center in his quarters. "Tuscon
Prime." It is LEO PRIME's voice. "The meeting had not ended, why did
you send your teams out and you retire to your quarters. Is there
something going on that we all need to be aware of? And where is the
rest of your team?" There is a note of concern in his voice as well as
agitation.

-------------------------------

RODIMUS PRIME drove through the different halls of the ARK, using the
its sensors as well as his own to locate the wayward WHEELIE,
"WHEELIE! Where are you?" He called out as he zoomed in what he
thought was his locatioons. "Wheelie!" He called again.

-------------------------------

In the room where the meeting was still suppose to be taking place LEO
PRIME was still looking at the the bot with the predacon signature,
still waiting for an answer to his last question.
